      "author": "Megan345 (Megan)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi Russ,</p>\n<p>You could consider adding a formula column that always displays today’s date, then adding that column into the update automation, along with any other text you require.</p>\n<p>Formula column:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/1/0/1057cbf271bc8a0f65f7af6c83ec7fa4b8018624.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/1/0/1057cbf271bc8a0f65f7af6c83ec7fa4b8018624.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"421\" height=\"181\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">421×181 6.22 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Automation example:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/f/0fbb35f0ff7a21ec3a04c57b4e9e89dd0a072d31.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/f/0fbb35f0ff7a21ec3a04c57b4e9e89dd0a072d31_2_690x267.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"267\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">917×355 19 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Resultant update after triggering the automation:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/e/5/e54ccb61c6699275c328a8d2fae70736102b8130.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/e/5/e54ccb61c6699275c328a8d2fae70736102b8130.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"390\" height=\"372\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">390×372 13.9 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
